graphql.query:
mutation {
  CreateTestimonial(
    input: {
      title: "Exilent!!!!"
      email: "neel.peater@mageinic.com"
      first_name: "Neel"
      last_name: "Peater"
      designation: "Developer"
      company: "MageINIC"
      website: "http://mageinic.com"
      rating: 5
      uploaded_file: {
        image_name: "male-icon.png"
        image_base64: ""
      }
      content: "<p>I found the image gallery plugin for a while. We need a module that we can add an image gallery to the product page. Finally, I found this and bought this. To be honest, I had a few trouble with installation but the support helped me get through it</p>"
    }
  ) {
    testimonial_id
    title
    content
    designation
    first_name
    last_name
    email
    image_name
    image_url
    rating
    company
    website
  }
}

  }
